---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projects | MoreBetterLabs"
  description="MoreBetterLabs projects: Ruzuku online course platform, The Business of Courses, and the Course Lab Podcast."
  canonical="/projects/"
>
  <section class="bg-stone-50 border-b border-stone-200 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Our Work
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
        Everything we build starts from the same question: how do we help people learn better?
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-16">

      <!-- Ruzuku -->
      <div class="group">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 mb-2">Flagship Product</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com" class="hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors" rel="noopener">
            Ruzuku
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          An online course platform designed around learning science, not just content delivery.
          Ruzuku's step-by-step course structure, built-in discussions, and completion-focused design
          grew directly from research on how adults actually learn — including my work on
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/how-it-works" class="text-teal-700 underline decoration-teal-300 hover:decoration-teal-500" rel="noopener">context-aware educational systems</a>
          and reflective learning metadata.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-500 space-y-1 mb-4">
          <li>75,000+ courses hosted since 2011</li>
          <li>500,000+ students served worldwide</li>
          <li>Zero transaction fees — we never take a cut of your revenue</li>
          <li>Built-in email, discussions, and live workshops</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com" class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 hover:underline" rel="noopener">
            Visit Ruzuku &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/features" class="text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline" rel="noopener">
            See features
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/pricing" class="text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline" rel="noopener">
            Pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-stone-200" />

      <!-- Book -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 mb-2">Book</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Business-Courses-Abe-Crystal/dp/1737374218" class="hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            The Business of Courses
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Everything I've learned from 13+ years helping course creators build sustainable online
          teaching businesses. Covers course design, pricing, launch strategy, student transformation,
          and building for the long term.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">
          Published 2021 · Available on Amazon ·
          <a href="https://www.ruzuku.com/learn/book" class="text-teal-700 hover:underline" rel="noopener">Free chapter summaries on Ruzuku</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-stone-200" />

      <!-- Podcast -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 mb-2">Podcast</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <a href="https://courselab.co/" class="hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Course Lab Podcast
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Weekly conversations with co-host Ari Iny about course creation, learning design,
          and building sustainable online teaching businesses. Produced in partnership with
          <a href="https://mirasee.com" class="text-teal-700 underline decoration-teal-300 hover:decoration-teal-500" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mirasee</a>.
        </p>
        <a href="https://courselab.co/" class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 hover:underline" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Listen to episodes &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-stone-200" />

      <!-- Learning Design Hub -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 mb-2">Research & Writing</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
          <a href="/learning-design/" class="hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors">
            Learning Design Hub
          </a>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Research-backed articles on learning design for practitioners. Translating learning science
          into practical frameworks for course creators — grounded in my academic research at UNC, NC State,
          and UCLA, and tested through thousands of courses on Ruzuku.
        </p>
        <a href="/learning-design/" class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-700 hover:underline">
          Read articles &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
